          This mean that the hacker will attempt to unlock it with every word as key key in the dictionery.
          Cryptanalysis means that we find the words with high frequency.
          It was called the indecipherable cipher for a good reason.
          Kasinki examination. This cipher was regarded as unbreakable until charles baggage broke it but never published his papaer.
          Identify the patterns of three or more characters. Write down the begining position of each pattern.
          Compute the differences between the starting point and the ending point. Determine all the factors for the differences.
          Key is one of the most common factors.
        </p>
      </div>

